            "is_accepted": false,
            "last_activity_date": 1464856618,
            "creation_date": 1464856618,
            "body": "<p>You can try <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>NodeList iDNodes = (Account).getElementsByTagName(\"Id\");\nint lengthofID = value1Nodes.getLength();\n\nif(lengthofID &gt; 0){\n //..proceed\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>alternatively similar is <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>doc.getChildNodes().item(0).getChildNodes().getLength();\n<\/code><\/pre>\n",
            "answer_id": 37586665,
